WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.140 --> 00:00:02.270
Mayli, umid qilamanki
bu o‘ta qiyin emas edi.

00:00:02.270 --> 00:00:03.780
Siz textColor atributidan ilgari foydalangansiz.

00:00:03.780 --> 00:00:08.070
Endi, bu qiymat nima ekanligini eslatib o‘tamiz,

00:00:08.070 --> 00:00:12.930
biz standart Android ranglariga kirish uchun @android:Color dan foydalanamiz,

00:00:12.930 --> 00:00:17.560
keyin /white biz Android-ning oq rangidan 
foydalanmoqchi ekanligimizni bildiradi.

00:00:17.560 --> 00:00:20.460
Darhaqiqat, Android standart 
imkoniyatlari unchalik ko‘p emas.

00:00:20.460 --> 00:00:23.390
Agar sizga ma’lum bir rang kerak bo‘lsa,
 hex kodni ishlatish juda oson,

00:00:23.390 --> 00:00:25.310
biz darsda gaplashgandek.

00:00:25.310 --> 00:00:28.870
 Hex kodlari uchun yaxshi manba bu
 material design ranglari veb-sahifasi

00:00:28.870 --> 00:00:30.800
Android ishlab chiqaruvchisi veb-saytidan.

00:00:30.800 --> 00:00:32.522
Ushbu veb-sahifa instruktor qaydlarida havola etilgan,

00:00:32.522 --> 00:00:34.470
agar siz unga ko‘z tashlamoqchi bo‘lsangiz.

00:00:34.470 --> 00:00:35.348
Bo‘ldi rang haqida etarlicha gaplashdik.

00:00:35.348 --> 00:00:36.740
Biz Android-ning oq rangidan foydalanmoqdamiz, va

00:00:36.740 --> 00:00:40.210
uning ko‘rinishini ko‘rish uchun
 Android Studio ga o‘tamiz.

00:00:40.210 --> 00:00:44.270
Mayli, eski qadrdon activity_main.xml fayliga boramiz

00:00:44.270 --> 00:00:46.660
siz atributlarni qo‘shishga odatlangandirsiz,
shuning uchun men davom etaman va

00:00:46.660 --> 00:00:50.070
Happy Birthday Ben matnli TextView ga 
yozishni boshlayman.

00:00:50.070 --> 00:00:51.885
Takrorlayman, men textColor 
atributidan foydalanyapman.

00:00:53.050 --> 00:00:55.876
Yaxshi, endi dropdown menyu menga 
ba’zi variantlarni beradi.

00:00:55.876 --> 00:00:59.792
Bu @Android:,

00:00:59.792 --> 00:01:05.750
keyin color/white va
deyarli darhol preview yangilanadi,

00:01:05.750 --> 00:01:08.950
oq bo‘ladi, bunda uni ko‘rish qiyin.

00:01:08.950 --> 00:01:10.290
Ammo yana biz xohlagan bir narsa.

00:01:10.290 --> 00:01:13.976
Mayli, endi shularni ikkinchi matn TextView 
bilan ham qilamiz.

00:01:13.976 --> 00:01:17.009
Bu erga bosing,

00:01:17.009 --> 00:01:21.944
android: textColor = "".

00:01:21.944 --> 00:01:29.273
Qo‘shtirnoq juda muhim, @android:/color .

00:01:30.390 --> 00:01:31.660
Men buni yozishni tugatgandan so‘ng,

00:01:31.660 --> 00:01:34.270
bu TextView ham ko‘rinmay qoladi.

00:01:35.290 --> 00:01:38.380
Bu kutilgan, chunki 
oq fonda oq matn ko‘rinmaydi, albatta.

00:01:39.460 --> 00:01:43.041
Ammo men view konturini bu 
yerda ko‘rayapman va

00:01:43.041 --> 00:01:46.950
bu u yerda matn borligidan darak beradi.

00:01:47.960 --> 00:01:51.510
Va puxtalik uchun, keling, buni bizning 
telefonlarimizda ishga tushiraylik.

00:01:51.510 --> 00:01:55.280
Mayli, buni uyda o‘tirganlar
ko‘rishi biroz qiyin bo‘lishi mumkin,

00:01:55.280 --> 00:01:58.820
faqat ochiq kulrang fonda matnni 
zo‘rg‘a ko‘rishim mumkin.

00:01:58.820 --> 00:02:00.570
Shunday qilib, biz yaxshi ish qildik.

00:02:00.570 --> 00:02:01.960
Bu bizning yana bitta ro‘yxatimiz.

00:02:01.960 --> 00:02:03.120
Keyingi bosqichga o‘tamiz.

